---
title: Honey Chipotle Shrimp Bowls with Black Bean Rice and Pepper Salsa
description: Jumbo shrimp tossed in a smoky sauce sits on top of black beans and rice in this fresh and vibrant dinner. Topped off with a roasted red pepper salsa with a hint of lime, this dish is packed with Mexican-inspired flavour.
